@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tylclt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos(0.81) + ((v2 + 0.43 + tmp + 0.40) * (v2 + 0.18 - tmp + 0.16)))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.69) + wp.cos(v0 + 0.26)) / 0.81)
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v0 + 0.43 + v1 + 0.90)))
    v1 = v1
    v2 = 0.27
    data[tid] = v0
